'''醫源病'''（{{lang-en|iatrogenesis}}，{{lang|en|iatrogenic artifact}}），又稱'''醫源性結果'''、'''醫源效應'''（{{lang|en|iatrogenic effect}}），通常是指因醫療意見、[[醫療|醫療]]過程、[[藥物治療|藥物治療]]或是[[醫療器材|醫療器材]]（Medical device），對[[病患|病患]]造成的不良影響（如[[疾病|疾病]]或[[併發症|併發症]]）。<ref name="thefreedictionary">{{cite web|url=http://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/Iatrogenesis|publisher=medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com|title=Iatrogenesis | definition of iatrogenesis by Medical dictionary|accessdate=2017-02-15|archive-date=2019-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719132234/https://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/iatrogenesis|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="merriam-webster">{{cite web|url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/medical/iatrogenesis|publisher=merriam-webster.com|title=Iatrogenesis Medical Definition | Merriam-Webster Medical Dictionary|accessdate=2017-02-15|archive-date=2018-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106190812/https://www.merriam-webster.com/medical/iatrogenesis|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="google">{{cite book|title=Medical Nemesis the expropriation of health|author1=Illich, I.|author2=Hose, R.|publisher=Elkrimbouziane|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=kUkjRSyWNmYC&pg=PA1967#v=onepage|page=1967|accessdate=2017-02-15|archive-date=2017-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216133851/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=kUkjRSyWNmYC&pg=PA1967#v=onepage|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="google2">{{cite book|title=What Dying People Want: Practical Wisdom For The End Of Life|author=Kuhl, D.|date=2003|publisher=PublicAffairs|isbn=9780786725830|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=QfiLuC7a47sC&pg=PA55#v=onepage|page=55|accessdate=2017-02-15|archive-date=2019-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217031649/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=QfiLuC7a47sC&pg=PA55#v=onepage|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="google3">{{cite book|title=Idea of Social Structure, the|author=Coser, L.A.|date=1975|publisher=Harcourt Brace Jovanovich|isbn